				<strong>Monetary</strong>
				<p>
				Donations are used to provide necessary materials for BAGEP workshops and educational scholarships for indigent BAGEP participants who would otherwise be unable to further their education. Donations are tax deductible. No dollar amount is too big or too small. All monetary gifts are greatly appreciated and help BAGEP youth.
				</P>
