		</div>
		
		<div class="div_texts mission_text">
			<p>
				The Boys and Girls Empowerment Program (BAGEP) is devoted to improving the lives of disenfranchised African children by teaching them essential life-building skills. Our focus is on helping this generation of children overcome the effects of marginalization by developing their self-esteem, catering to their mental and physical health, and supporting their education. BAGEP aims to encourage young people to realize their true potential as future leaders who are able to change their communities and their country.
